query:
select
                    valid_from as "valid_from!: DateTime",
                    valid_until as "valid_until?: DateTime",
                    json(value) as "value!: sqlx::types::Json<DemandCurveDto>"
                from
                    curve_data
                where
                    demand_id = $1
                and
                    ($2 is null or valid_from >= $2)
                and
                    ($3 is null or valid_until is null or valid_until < $3)
                and
                    value is not null
                order by
                    valid_from desc
                limit $4
